    "test_coverage_evidence": 8,
    "ui_visual_design": 9
  },
  "composite_arithmetic_mean": 8.7,
  "verdict": "WIN_LIKELY",
  "blocking_gaps_for_10_10": [
    {
      "category": "test_coverage_evidence",
      "gap": "Claimed 802/802 tests in project facts but trust bar and demo explicitly show 623/623 engine tests; also no visible regression harness output or NTI cohort test logs in demo.",
      "smallest_fix": "Update all references (trust bar, README, demo) to a single verified number and embed a one-click 'run tests' button that prints the 802/802 summary."
    },
    {
      "category": "documentation_polish",
      "gap": "Mermaid diagrams and invariants.md are referenced but flows.json/arch_mind.json/bitnet_pairs.json are external fetches; no inline README excerpt or full architecture.md content visible.",
      "smallest_fix": "Embed the full architecture.md and clinicalmem_invariants.md as collapsible sections in the demo or add a 'View full docs' modal with the Mermaid source."
    },
    {
      "category": "demo_quality_judge_wow",
      "gap": "Safety check, what-if simulator, BitNet classify, and federation mock are all client-side simulations with no live backend call or real engine execution shown.",
      "smallest_fix": "Add a visible 'Connect to live engine' toggle that hits a real /api endpoint (even if mocked server-side) and shows actual latency + hash computation."
    }
  ],
  "strengths": [
    "Hero animation with rotating audit-chain rings, staggered layer dots, and landing 'CONTRAINDICATED' stamp is genuinely impressive and healthcare-appropriate in 5 seconds.",
    "Deep clinical standards integration (FHIR R4 with NPI-validated practitioners, RxNorm/SNOMED/UMLS, 21 typed federation invariants) backed by verified MD co-author.",
    "Reproducibility primitives (Merkle chain, Ed25519, plan_hash replay, BitNet Q16.16) are wired end-to-end and demoed with in-browser SHA-256 verification."
  ],
  "delta_from_round_3": "R3 UI score collapsed to 6.00 because the GitHub repo went private and no demo.html was visible. R4 supplies the full 2125-line live demo source, enabling direct scoring of typography (Lexend + Fraunces + JetBrains Mono), custom trust/premium/po palettes, animated rings, interactive what-if + BitNet replay, and Mermaid flows. This single change lifts ui_visual_design from 6 to 9 and demo_quality_judge_wow from low to 9. Additional deltas: ASCII diagrams replaced by Mermaid, federation contract now explicitly shows X25519 + ChaCha20-Poly1305 wrapping before MIC@2 serialization, and arch-mind L1 9/9 + Phase B invariants documented. Composite rises from 8.72 to 8.7 with the UI recovery outweighing minor test-number inconsistency."
}

